description: California Taco Bear is a company born from a love of good times and great food. Started by two friends who grew up in sunny California, this truck strives to bring the best quality food and fun the sunshine state has to offer, serving world-inspired tacos with a CA flair. Meat, poultry, seafood, and veggie tacos are all available at this charming truck, and each flavor is named after an LA neighborhood. Stop by the California Taco Bear truck, and take a bite out of Hollywood!
name: California Taco Bear
